                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="12532209" author="knutanders" created="Wed, 3 Oct 2007 20:27:02 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;I see the same failure on OpenSolaris when I run the test with locale set to no_NO.ISO8859-1@nynorsk.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12532212" author="knutanders" created="Wed, 3 Oct 2007 20:37:33 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;The attached patch replaces a call to Double.parseDouble() with NumberFormat.parse(). NumberFormat uses the current locale when it parses the number and therefore also works in non-English locales. I have successfully run TableFunctionTest with locale set to en_US and no_NO.ISO8859-1@nynorsk with this patch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
